---
title: Hearty Tomato & Chorizo Orecchiette with Parmesan
description: Cheesy, rich and red, it’s a tomato sauce that’s very easy on the tastebuds. There’s tomato and leek stirred through alongside
mild chorizo, toss everything in a bowl of orecchiette pasta and dinner just became irresistible.
